{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1679a625b6","title":"派人侦察宁夏及缓远等地敌情","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"46692904c0","index":0,"year":1936,"month":10,"day":5,"articleId":"1679a625b6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fb2b3bfef0","type":"paragraph","text":"派人侦察宁夏及缓远等地敌情！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"1679a625b6"},{"id":"5dd04f0176","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年10月5日）罗迈，宋、宋：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"1679a625b6"},{"id":"01d4cdf076","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、立即派妥人分两次出发（装做生意的），经宁夏直到阿拉善旗达王根据地之定远营，确实侦察该地日本人修建机场、储存飞机情形，该地城堡高厚程度，达王步骑蒙兵数目及宁夏到该地沿途里程、房屋、关溢等情形。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"1679a625b6"},{"id":"70e75de464","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、宁夏绥远两处日本人是否已筑飞机场及设特务机关，亦派人专查。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"1679a625b6"},{"id":"d8227975a5","type":"paragraph","text":"丙、上两项限十一月五日以前报告我丁、张心余十一月五日须到定边待命。并请立即函张将他所","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"1679a625b6"},{"id":"f64f02e277","type":"paragraph","text":"[111936年9月，中共中央为实现夺取宁夏的战略计划，专门成立了定边工作委员会，从事夺取宁夏的准备工作。这是毛泽东给中共定边工作委员会书记罗迈（李维汉）、红军第二十八军军长宋时轮和政治委员宋任穷的电报。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"1679a625b6"},{"id":"d3ef81b472","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]达王，当时任宁夏阿拉善旗旗长、国民党军阿拉善旗区防司令部司令。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"1679a625b6"},{"id":"de36211d36","type":"paragraph","text":"131定远营，也称定远城，俗称主爷府，即今内蒙古自治区阿拉善左旗巴彦浩特镇。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"1679a625b6"},{"id":"0fa28fe28f","type":"paragraph","text":"141绥远，旧省名，韩今内蒙古自治区中部地区，1954年撤销。[5]张心余，即张德生，中共三边特委书记。知宁夏至定远营道路、房屋、关溢及定远营之一切情形先期妥报你处。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"1679a625b6"},{"id":"119b2447b9","type":"paragraph","text":"毛五号十五时","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"1679a625b6"}],"page":{"id":"41d3e7346e","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"1679a625b6","start":199,"end":200}}}},"__N_SSG":true}